source.name: Oregon Marine Board Strategic Plan 2011-2016
source.description: The Oregon State Marine Board has a new strategic plan, based on customer feedback from an online survey, blog and town hall meetings.  This comprehensive plan is a new chart and Marine Board staff, with the help of Board Member Champions, are setting a new course for Your boating agency...
